Problem: Power of Three
Topic: Math
Difficulty: Easy

Approach:
If n is less than or equal to 0, return false. Otherwise, repeatedly divide n by 3 while it is divisible by 3. If the final value becomes 1, then n is a power of three; otherwise, it is not.

Time Complexity: O(log₃ n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

Code:
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPowerOfThree(int n) {
        if(n<=0){
            return false;
        }
        while(n%3==0){
            n/=3;
        }
        return n==1;
    }
};
